OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781795476
OL,3,CThree arrested after cannabis worth
OL,4,C#139 million seized
OL,6,FThree people have been arrested after
OL,7,Fwhat police have dubbed their "biggest
OL,8,Fcannabis seizure ever" worth #139
OL,9,Fmillion.
OL,11,FTwo men and one woman from Merthyr
OL,12,FTydfil, Ebbw Vale, and Abertillery
OL,13,Fhave been arrested on Tuesday 16th
OL,14,FJune.
OL,16,FAll three suspects, aged in their 30s
OL,17,Fand 40s, were arrested on suspicion of
OL,18,Ffacilitating the importations and are
OL,19,Fcurrently in police custody.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
