OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781795476
OL,3,CThree arrested after cannabis worth
OL,4,C#139 million seized
OL,6,FThe drugs were being transported from
OL,7,FCanada to Southampton Port, but were
OL,8,Fintercepted by the Canada Border
OL,9,FServices Agency (CBSA).
OL,11,FIn a joint investigation approximately
OL,12,F12 tonnes of cannabis was discovered
OL,13,Finside two shipping containers.
OL,15,FThe operation was a joint effort
OL,16,Fbetween the Canada Border Services
OL,17,FAgency, UK Border Force, and the South
OL,18,FWest Regional Organised Crime Unit,
OL,19,Fwith local support from both South
OL,20,FWales Police and Gwent Police.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
