PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781795476
OL,3,CThree arrested after cannabis worth
OL,4,C#139 million seized
OL,6,FActing Inspector Stuart Cumine, from
OL,7,FSWROCU, said the operation had taken a
OL,8,F"huge amount of drugs out of
OL,9,Fcirculation" and hit criminal gangs
OL,10,Fwhere it hurts most.
OL,12,F"While cannabis can commonly be
OL,13,Fperceived as a low-level threat,
OL,14,Fpeople need to understand that the
OL,15,Fcriminals importing and supplying it
OL,16,Fare using the substantial profits to
OL,17,Ffund other criminality," he said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
