CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781795476
OL,3,CThree arrested after cannabis worth
OL,4,C#139 million seized
OL,6,F"Operations like this, working with
OL,7,Fpartners on a national and
OL,8,Finternational level, disrupt these
OL,9,Fcriminal networks, deprive them of
OL,10,Ffunds, and protect communities across
OL,11,Fthe UK."
OL,13,FBorder Force Director General, Phil
OL,14,FDouglas said: "This biggest cannabis
OL,15,Fseizure ever shows Border Force's
OL,16,Frelentless action to stop drugs
OL,17,Freaching UK streets and destroying
OL,18,Flives.
OL,26,@vD@OOU
