OL,3,CThree arrested after cannabis worth
OL,4,C#139 million seized
OL,6,F"My thanks to our officers, the South
OL,7,FWest Regional Organised Crime Unit,
OL,8,Fand the Canada Border Services Agency
OL,9,Ffor their dedication, collaboration,
OL,10,Fand professionalism."
